Title: We Will Part
Writer: Pablo Fernandez, Pablo Fernandez, Roberth Nordh (story), Siham Shurafa (story), Kerim Troeller (story)
Actors: Kerim Troeller, Siham Shurafa, Lona Nilsson, Jasmin Farran
Plot: A film about a young man, a woman, and the few days they are forced to spend together in a remote cabin in Sweden.
